g.text: Page Header Fields Memory Layout | 8 bytes (Leaf) / 12 bytes (Internal)
FirstFreeblock (uint16): Offset to first freeblock chain, 0 if none
CellCount (uint16): Number of cells stored on this page
CellContentStart (uint16): Offset to cell content area start, 0 means 65536
FragmentedBytes (uint8): Count of fragmented free bytes within cell area
RightMostPointer (uint32): Rightmost child page number (INTERNAL PAGES ONLY)

text.tspan: Note: RightMostPointer stores page number of rightmost child
for B-tree traversal when no left pointer matches
